<h1><strong>《平安经》</strong></h1>
<p class="ql-align-center"><strong>有讽</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center">荣西安</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">慢道平安水笔涂，平安二字换阿谀。</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">吾今念诵平安卷，不被醍醐被浆糊。</p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><strong>有讽</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center">范东学</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">书成句句颂平安，得此佛心今太难。</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">教我儿孙皆效仿，或能入仕到厅官。</p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><strong>全民热议《平安经》戏作</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center">郑万才</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">闻言东北有厅官，作著三千乃大观。</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">一自平安名世后，不知怎样保平安！</p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><strong>题《平安经》</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center">柳茂恒</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">鸿经一卷颂平安，墨海滔滔恐蘸干。</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">虚弱何堪经霹雳，料知酷暑已身寒。</p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><strong>平安经</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center">黄训鲲</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">下属频传贺电声，好书自可促民生。</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">人人深念平安调，保尔明天不痛经。</p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><strong>平安经</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center">金嗣水</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">巨著皇皇成大观，联珠屁话造金丹。</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">高俅蹴鞠得恩宠，博士溜须步步官。</p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><strong>戏说《平安经》</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center">王力田</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">拍案惊奇势不孤，平安经卷热当垆。</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">省城破戒羞三藏，博士开颜得万铢。</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">但使思潮通秘诀，全凭赘语祭灵符。</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">传媒炒作芳菲尽，或许厅官毁仕途。</p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><strong>平安经</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center">常玉山</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">高官何事写真经，智障脑残也副厅。</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">不是有司干涉早，此君恐怕又高升。</p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><strong>《平安经》事感言</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center">杨非木</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">满纸平安好笑多，居然一夜俏山河。</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">他年我若为厅长，也著经书几万箩。</p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><strong>喜读《平安经》</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center">张承训</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">忽于网络见神经，愚昧顿消心眼明。</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">只恨早年无此作，误我为官到省厅。</p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><strong>戏说《平安经》（新韵）</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center">高常贵</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">位重权高坐省厅，从来颐使未言轻。</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">平安二字传天下，势盖四书和五经。</p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p0.itc.cn/images01/20200731/d6955e90987c41e4bf21a187bedc5fab.jpeg" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-center">（《平安经》书页）</p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><strong>戏题《平安经》（新韵）</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center">赵士红</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">博导著书谁敢轻，平安页页码分明。</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">若非官位称厅副，可有吹嘘马屁精？</p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><strong>闻吉林某高官《平安经》一书被封</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center">王书明</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">道是无声亦有声，平安经又惹人惊。</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">东南西北皆怀爱，春夏秋冬更有情。</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">身在庙堂忙造句，梦归艺苑巧留名。</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">若非官帽金光闪，何处寻来马屁精。</p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><strong>《平安经》出版有感(新韵)</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center">放空心灵</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">自古尘民图饱餐，从来华贵望平安。</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">声声马屁文书里，权富之人谁不奸？</p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><strong>戏题《平安经》</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center">赵仁波</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">平安二字众人求，巨作横飞出版羞。</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">怎奈高官闲不得，修书卖弄赚金油。</p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><strong>讽《平安经》（三首）</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center">王瑾（河北邯郸）</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">一</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">巨著皇皇不是书，心明读者未糊涂。</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">智商纵使无多少，能被无端侮辱不？</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">二</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">巨著皇皇不是书，平安两字弄玄乎。</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">糟蹋纸墨知多少，可讨一回公道无？</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">三</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">巨著皇皇不是书，蠢猪方下蠢功夫。</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">孔明再把王朗骂，极品厚颜无耻徒。</p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p4.itc.cn/images01/20200731/0bd99adb3b0145b2a60559b40998ea54.jpeg" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"> （《平安经》书页）</p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><strong>平安经</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center">长青山人</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">墨水流干笔未停，文坛浪起不安宁。</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">看君打坐云楼里，无甚修为也著经。</p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><strong>读《平安经》（新声）</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center">刘增辉</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">北语南言左右声，再说爱恨要分清。</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">红尘染尽乌纱帽，戴上能书万字经。</p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><strong>读《平安经》</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center">刘增辉</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">念起平安如斩钉，此经念与国人听。</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">一经万字留真爱，三字应随万字经。</p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><strong>哀贺电厅长之《平安经》</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center">花之蝶</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">马屁精堂多捧杀，丢人丢到省厅家。</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">字如累卵麻坛摆，赞似繁星拇指加。</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">但使一朋忠谏尔，断无百损乐开花。</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">墨香难近科班吏，观此经书笑掉牙。</p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><strong>也说《平安经》</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center">杨焕</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">乱来一卷说平安，满纸荒唐谁敢看。</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">自古公门应不二，私心克尽果无端。</p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><strong>戏说平安经（新韵）</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center">孙艳梅</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">素紽标异著经籍，题作平安卷帙奇。</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">着墨平安多次幂，国人遍送乃还余。</p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><strong>戏说《平安经》</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center">傅国志</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">独门神技搅波澜，惊掉下巴铺满滩。</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">千古真知成粪土，一朝骇俗看厅官。</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">但凭拍马溜须众，何患扬名立万难。</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">云涌风来无足惧，诸君随我数平安。</p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><strong>戏说《平安经》三题(新韵)</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center">计德辉</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">(一)</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">另类厅官成网红，平安当下最流行。</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">世人多把平安道，说是平安不怕重。</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">(二)</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">经书句句道平安，云里山即雾里山。</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">如问此君新创意，平安二字用得欢。</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">(三)</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">如不出书枉在朝，为官也要赶时髦。</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">草成一本平安卷，另有它称叫吐槽。</p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><strong>戏说《平安经》（新韵）</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center">高常贵</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">位重权高坐省厅，从来颐使未言轻。</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">平安二字传天下，势盖四书和五经。</p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><strong>致《平安经》作者贺电六首</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center">田恒柱（湖北）</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">一</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">无聊至极饱三餐，博士先生两脑残。</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">更有闻踪追捧者，奉为巨著令心寒。</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">二</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">儒林巨制有多宽，不到长城不算完。</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">若把全书来概括，归于两字总平安。</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">三</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">歪书一本毁三观，合十求神辱警坛。</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">且问堂堂副厅长，念经岂可保平安。</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">四</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">堆词造句本辛酸，岂料查来令胆寒。</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">欲问何曾遭失算，悔初未写己平安。</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">五</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">自寻乐子自寻欢，不出经书实在难。</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">欲改前非须彻底，莫教后辈作昏官。</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">六</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">经文一念透心凉，料定斯时鬓上霜。</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">全国人民来贺电，金猴奋起不寻常。</p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p5.itc.cn/images01/20200731/1a92e261ea6845b2827c50ca0bec0954.jpeg" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><strong>电贺平安经</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center">发哥</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">头衔跨界著新经，名利双收欲未停。</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">莫借平安欺佛主，苍天不怒起雷霆。</p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><strong>贺电《平安经》上市二首</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center">霍德华</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">其一</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">博士双衔头上抗，平安一句入书堂。</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">官家面对吃瓜众，吹捧失灵嗝屁凉。</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">其二</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">高到头衔吓死人，出书上架为淘金。</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">翻开一页未曾睹，已是官名化土尘。</p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><strong>无题</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center">无名氏</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">去年火了老黄黄，今岁平安二字忙。</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">纸贵缘何名姓臭，憋诗痛苦在茅房。</p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><strong>粗读贺电所著《平安经》有感</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center">何跨海</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">鸿儒巨著毁三观，满纸纷嚣两字漫。</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">世上千般随后缀，人间万象置前端。</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">成时媒体皆为贺，赠处钱囊足尽欢。</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">传播更能凭网络，谁同作者祝平安。</p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><strong>赞贺电</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center">小愚哥</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">闲来无事著神经，平不平安赖贺厅。</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">若是世人皆信你，不神经也变神经。</p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><strong>题《平安经》</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center">平治散人</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">声声禅语道平安，贺电嘉评不一般。</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">贝页经文千古唱，奇葩博士万人观。</p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><strong>闻吉林“平安经”，有感而作</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center">南风</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">平安二字值千金，满卷平安不胜吟。</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">自古司空多见惯，难分鹿马到如今。</p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><strong>也题《平安经》</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center">程礼银（呈子） </p>
<p class="ql-align-center">重弹老调古今同，一曲平安造化工。</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">讨好声高谁顾脸，墙头有草总随风。</p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><strong>无题</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center">杨卓</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">经年百姓盼平安，谁解平安不一般。</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">燥热喧天无奈事，蝉虫不可祸心弹。</p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p8.itc.cn/images01/20200731/05caa3e121504a1f86106a7a21f9c5fc.jpeg" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-center">(网络漫画)</p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><strong>也说《平安经》</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center">韩瑞清</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">缘何满口念平安，莫是心怀魍魉寒。</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">白纸无辜成鬼咒，厅官废话倒三观。</p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><strong>《平安经》里祝平安（新韵）</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center">南国风笛</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">逢源任上做厅官，欲把光环使劲添。</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">一部经书方问世，谁知口水也翻船。</p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><strong>打油</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center">风</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">人逢盛世话平安，平安多了惹人烦。</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">最傻还是跟风者，不服你也做厅官。</p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><strong>无题</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center">瓣</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">一卷平安难再安，厅官慌诞近疯癫，</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">追名逐利著经典，怡笑大方成笑谈。</p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><strong>贺电官儿平安经</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center">郭庆澄</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">平安贺电戏连台，马屁生香出怪胎。</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">莫道官儿容易得，卖乖卖傻做奴才。</p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><strong>平安经</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center">肖定潭</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">平安国里出厅官，一本平安世面宽。</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">莫把平安搬嘴上，心怀德字最平安。</p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p2.itc.cn/images01/20200731/c572a9545007468c9cef5ac3400bdc93.jpeg" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><strong>《平安经》</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center">呆先生</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">一卷高吟惊破天，撷珠诺奖或明年。</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">何妨再缀吉祥句，添作平安姊妹篇。</p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><strong>《平安经》</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center">呆先生</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">一对平安一本书，厅官名气动三誉。</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">一千支笔写归写，十四亿人猪还猪。</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">只为厅官有贺电，直教老子悔当初。</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">来生我识两枚字，笑傲江湖应有余。</p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><strong>打油一首，愿众生平安</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center">江湖有你</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">厅长奇书谁比肩？平安两字贯通篇。</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">高官学者来传诵，一本正经念平安。</p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><strong>《平安经》感言</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center">王志军</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">今闻北处有高官，出本奇书众友欢。</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">二字平安谁与表？惹来百姓腹中寒。</p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><strong>闻《平安经》现世</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center">李进</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">贺电写来谁又看，满篇文字说平安。</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">风骚岂是癫狂意，老子闻之起浩叹。</p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><strong>戏说《平安经》</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center">许锦华</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">人做高官脑变形，平安经里念歪经。</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">全篇写尽荒唐诵，万句流空怪异聆。</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">可笑谀词拍马屁，疑惊网络捧洋星。</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">东风一扫斜风散，正气凌云荡省厅。</p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p6.itc.cn/images01/20200731/f4b0cdcfe86643dbb8c2a94237af3be3.jpeg" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"> （网络书法）</p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><strong>问贺电</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center">陈德永（河北）</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">厅官贺电颂平安，寡味清汤似快餐。</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">蠢事招来风浪起，声名扫地可心酸？</p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><strong>祈安</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center">云中峰</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">三藏孤行万里征，鉴真横渡苦求承。</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">平安一纸经文诵，只见朝官不见僧。</p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><strong>题平安经二首（新韵）</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center">孟庆和</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">其一</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">奇经一部总争新，厚土奇葩断古今。</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">百姓拈来发一问，频施雨露是何人。</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">其二</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">真经一部属何宗。一卷奇文气象雄。</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">而或师从鬼谷子，天庭降下一雷公。</p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><strong>读《平安经》</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center">孔繁都(浙江)</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">中华法律顺民心，平等双赢论古今。</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">和顺一门生百福，平安二字值千金。</p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><strong>贺电《平安经》</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center">郭通海</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">经书一部系平安，臭屁熏人也敛钱。</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">世道如今多怪事，难猜爆料是厅官。</p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><strong>无题(新韵)</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center">熊璞珩</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">经年倾力宣乡旅，实是言微骋管弦。</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">自古人生多舛运，入身忧患叹平安。</p>
<h1>《千家诗词》</h1>
<p>主编：郑万才</p>
<p>副主编：王惠玲、王天明、胡晓娜</p>
<p>编辑：胡敏、刘宴会、杨余龙、刘爱红、韦化彪</p>
